---
title: Miso Chili Chicken Wraps with Shredded Carrots
description: Obsessed with miso? Us too. That’s why we’re keeping all that precious umami flavor safe and sound in these miso chili chicken wraps! Fully cooked chicken breasts are chopped and tossed in a savory mix of miso sauce, spicy-sweet chili sauce, ponzu, and peanut butter. Next up, chicken and shredded carrots are wrapped up tight in a soft and secure tortilla. A tasty lunch AND peace of mind? Now that’s a wrap.
